    <p> Kliink empowers philanthropists (Like You!) and provides value to non-profit organizations by promoting them. Spreading the word through trusted sources often results in more donations than direct marketing alone. Creating buzz by sharing, commenting, and liking items can be more powerful than donations. The more actions you take to spread the word, the more “philanthropist” points you accumulate!
